snippet.title: Dude, Where Is My Beer? - Trailer 2020
snippet.description:
Buy "Dude, Where Is My Beer?" on Steam!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1288760/Dude_Where_Is_My_Beer/
Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/dude-where-is-my-beer-switch/
An old school point and click adventure game about finding a pilsner in the confusing world of unnecessary craft beers and snobby hipsters.

Web: https://www.dudewhereismybeer.com/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DudeWhereIsMyBeer/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/where_beer
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/dude_where_is_my_beer/
